OL,4,Ctwenties find friends after uni
OL,6,FShe said: "Social media can be an
OL,7,Famazing tool as it's connected all of
OL,8,Fus here.
OL,10,F"However, we know as well that it can
OL,11,Fbe really damaging. You usually only
OL,12,Fsee the good times of what goes on in
OL,13,Fpeople's lives and it can increase the
OL,14,Fproblem of poor mental health because
OL,15,Fyou feel you're missing out.
